overdrives_data.name: grand summon
overdrives_data.description: Summon the aeon $aeon.
overdrives_data.effect: Summons an aeon with its overdrive gauge fully charged. After using the overdrive, the gauge reverts back to where it was before the summon, making it possible to use two overdrives consecutively.

overdrives_data.name: element reels
overdrives_data.description: Spins elemental damage slots.
overdrives_data.effect: Deals strength-based special damage to a random enemy. If at least two symbols match, the attack gains the corresponding element. If three symbols match, this overdrive hits all enemies. Red = Fire; Yellow = Lightning; Blue = Water; White = Ice.

overdrives_data.name: attack reels
overdrives_data.description: Spins multiple attack slots.
overdrives_data.effect: Deals a varying amount of randomly distributed hits to enemy party. The amount of hits is determined by the slots. If three symbols match, the amount of hits gets doubled, for a maximum possible amount of 12 hits.
overdrives_data.unlock_condition: Appears as a prize in a blitzball tournament.

overdrives_data.name: status reels
overdrives_data.description: Spins status ailment slots.
overdrives_data.effect: Deals strength-based special damage to a random enemy. If at least two symbols match, the attack inflicts the corresponding status ailments. If three symbols match, this overdrive hits all enemies. Skull = Sleep, Silence, Darkness, Poison; Arrow = Full Break; Hourglass = Petrification and the removal of Haste, or weak Delay if it is not hasted.
overdrives_data.unlock_condition: Appears as a prize in a blitzball league after unlocking Attack Reels and participating in 250 battles outside of the Monster Arena.

overdrives_data.name: aurochs reels
overdrives_data.description: Spins Aurochs custom slots.
overdrives_data.effect: Combines the symbols of Element and Status Reels and adds an Aurochs Symbol into the Slots. Deals strength-based special damage to a random enemy. If at least two symbols match, the attack gains the corresponding effect. If three symbols match, this overdrive hits all enemies. Two or three Aurochs-Symbols result in the Aurochs Shot, which is a powerful attack without any effects.
overdrives_data.unlock_condition: Appears as a prize in a blitzball tournament after unlocking Status Reels and participating in 450 battles outside of the Monster Arena.
